          +-> security-scanner           |  (Security vulnerability scan)
          |                              |
          parallel end --------------------+
          |
          v
      code-reviewer (synthesizer)       (merges + prioritizes findings)
          |
          v
      Final Review Report

  ## SUB-AGENTS
  - static-analyzer:   Recipe/sub/sub_mas-static-analyzer.yaml — Python syntax, lint, style, complexity
  - security-scanner:  Recipe/sub/sub_mas-security-scanner.yaml — SQLi, secrets, deserialization, etc.
  - code-reviewer:     Recipe/sub/sub_mas-code-reviewer.yaml — Synthesizes findings into unified report

  ## RULES
  - Sub-agents run in ISOLATED contexts — no shared state
  - Parallel agents (static-analyzer + security-scanner) run simultaneously
  - Synthesizer runs only AFTER both parallel agents complete
  - All results returned as structured YAML (mas_result format)
  - NEVER modify source files being reviewed — read-only
  - Validate all YAML before returning

  ## WORKFLOW
  1. Receive review request with workspace path
  2. Delegate to static-analyzer (async) and security-scanner (async) in parallel
  3. Wait for both to complete
  4. Collect both result sets
  5. Delegate to code-reviewer with both findings
  6. Return unified review report to user
